After a brief absence from the music scene, Mavin Records singer, D’Prince returns with a new tune titled “ Lavida “. This time, D’Prince features the new kid on the bloc, Rema who delivered on the wonderful track. Since his unveiling as Mavin Records’ artiste, Rema has been a topic on the lips of both music lovers and critics. But we are more concerned about you watching the Lavida video than the Dumebi crooner, at the moment. So hit the play button below! 